<li class="goods-col">

<a target="_self" href="/product/detail/13111/5222252/31">
<div class="goods-col_img">
<img src="https://img.furusato-tax.jp/img/x/product/details/20181108/pd_66ad8d45a1719dfc333d276b0da565685cacec93.jpg" alt="サンプル写真" class="goods-col_photo" decoding="async" />
